    <h3>June 2026 &mdash; Will Eesley's death year corrected from 1979 to 1986</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Source of the correction: Chuck Eesley, June 2026.</strong>
    </p>
    <p>
      A draft version of the
      <a href="/family/wilbur-eesley/">Will Eesley page</a> and several pages
      that referenced him had carried his death as <em>1979</em>. Will died
